# This repo uses npm (single root package-lock.json). A stray pnpm-lock.yaml
# or bun.lock only creates a second, drifting dependency graph that security
# scanners flag for CVEs the npm build never installs (e.g. a phantom Next.js
# pin, or a stale `ws` in packages/remotion/bun.lock). Keep them out.
pnpm-lock.yaml
bun.lock
